[SN]TITLE[SN]
Singapore pupils to clean up schools

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
New rules mean children in Singapore will be expected to help clean their school as part of their day.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
16 March 2016 Last updated at 06:40 GMT
It's hoped pupils will learn to care for their own space and shared areas, and learn good habits for the future.
We asked some kids here in the UK what they thought of the idea...
